JOHANNESBURG - An empowerment initiative is helping young women succeed in their businesses.She Leads Africa helps build entrepreneurs' careers by hosting events across the continent.Its vision is to become the number one destination for smart and ambitious young women.Founded by Afua Osei and Yasmin Belo-Osagie in 2014, the She Leads Africa enterprise is trying to figure out how to get more women on the African continent into the driver s seat.* Watch the full video report by Busi Lethole in the gallery above.eNCA